﻿<!doctype html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Приложение Д — Форма №1</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #000000;
    }

    .page {
      width: 1200px;
      margin: 24px auto;
      padding: 8px 10px 24px;
    }

    .top-note {
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.25;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .top-note .sub {
      display: block;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .top-note .form {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 2px;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .main-title {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.25;
      margin: 14px 0 18px;
    }

    .line-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
      align-items: end;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .line-block {
      min-height: 48px;
    }

    .line {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
      height: 22px;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .line-caption {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-top: 6px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .line-caption.nowrap { white-space: nowrap; }

    .line-center-text {
      align-self: center;
      font-size: 18px;
      padding: 0 8px;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .length-row {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin: 10px 0 16px;
    }

    .inline-line {
      display: inline-block;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
      min-width: 60px;
      height: 20px;
      vertical-align: baseline;
    }

    table.form-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      table-layout: fixed;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .form-table th,
    .form-table td {
      border: 1px solid #000;
      padding: 6px 4px;
      vertical-align: middle;
      word-wrap: break-word;
    }

    .form-table th {
      font-weight: 700;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .form-table .left {
      text-align: left;
    }

    .form-table .num-row td {
      height: 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .form-table .data-row td {
      height: 50px;
    }

    .form-table .w1  { width: 8%; }
    .form-table .w2  { width: 8%; }
    .form-table .w3  { width: 8%; }
    .form-table .w4  { width: 8%; }
    .form-table .w5  { width: 8%; }
    .form-table .w6  { width: 8%; }
    .form-table .w7  { width: 8%; }
    .form-table .w8  { width: 8%; }
    .form-table .w9  { width: 8%; }
    .form-table .w10 { width: 8%; }
    .form-table .w11 { width: 8%; }
    .form-table .w12 { width: 8%; }

    .total-row {
      margin-top: 14px;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .total-line {
      display: inline-block;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
      min-width: 120px;
      height: 20px;
      vertical-align: baseline;
    }

    @media print {
      body {
        background: #fff;
      }

      .page {
        width: auto;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <div class="top-note">
      Приложение Д
      <span class="sub">Формы анализа данных о дорожно-транспортных происшествиях</span>
      <span class="form">Форма № 1</span>
    </div>

    <div class="main-title">
      Оценка тенденций изменения основных показателей аварийности на УДС,
      находящейся в ведении
    </div>

    <div class="line-row">
      <div class="line-block">
        <div class="line"></div>
        <div class="line-caption">(Владелец автомобильными дорогами)</div>
      </div>

      <div class="line-center-text">за</div>

      <div class="line-block">
        <div class="line"></div>
        <div class="line-caption nowrap">Период учета (квартал, полугодие, девять месяцев, год)</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="length-row">
      Общая протяженность УДС
      <span class="inline-line"></span>
      км
      <span class="inline-line" style="min-width: 40px;"></span>
      м
    </div>

    <table class="form-table">
      <tr>
        <th class="w1" rowspan="3">№<br>п\п</th>
        <th class="w2" rowspan="3">Наименование<br>дороги<br>(улицы)</th>
        <th class="w3" rowspan="3">Годы</th>

        <th colspan="4" class="left">Сведения о ДТП</th>

        <th colspan="5" class="left">
          Сведения о ДТП, в местах совершения которых установлены
          недостатки транспортно-эксплуатационного состояния УДС
        </th>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <th class="w4 left" rowspan="2">Количество ДТП</th>
        <th class="w5 left" rowspan="2">Ранено,<br>чел.</th>
        <th class="w6 left" rowspan="2">Погибло,<br>чел.</th>
        <th class="w7 left" rowspan="2">Показатель тяжести последствий ДТП</th>

        <th colspan="2" class="left">Количество ДТП</th>
        <th class="w10 left" rowspan="2">Ранено,<br>чел.</th>
        <th class="w11 left" rowspan="2">Погибло,<br>чел.</th>
        <th class="w12 left" rowspan="2">Показатель тяжести последствий ДТП</th>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <th class="w8 left">Всего</th>
        <th class="w9 left">В % от общего количества ДТП</th>
      </tr>

      <tr class="num-row">
        <td class="left">1</td>
        <td class="left">2</td>
        <td class="left">3</td>
        <td class="left">4</td>
        <td class="left">5</td>
        <td class="left">6</td>
        <td class="left">7</td>
        <td class="left">8</td>
        <td class="left">9</td>
        <td class="left">10</td>
        <td class="left">11</td>
        <td class="left">12</td>
      </tr>

      <tr class="data-row">
        <td rowspan="3" class="left">1.</td>
        <td rowspan="3">&nbsp;</td>
        <td class="left">АППГ</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>3
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="data-row">
        <td class="left">Период учета</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="data-row">
        <td class="left">(+/-, %%)</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
      </tr>

      <tr class="data-row">
        <td rowspan="3" class="left">2.</td>
        <td rowspan="3">&nbsp;</td>
        <td class="left">АППГ</td>
        <td>{{}}</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="data-row">
        <td class="left">Период учета</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="data-row">
        <td class="left">(+/-, %%)</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <div class="total-row">
      Итого за период учета:
      <span class="total-line"></span>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
